---
---

<main class="hero">
  <div class="bg"></div>

  <section class="content" aria-label="Reference splash">
    <img
      class="logo"
      src="/brand/reference-logo.svg"
      alt="Reference — Supersonic Creative"
    />

    <p class="about">
      Hello.<br /><br />
      We're a couple of creative directors. Born in MENA. Raised in the UK.
      Trusted by some of the best in the region.<br /><br />
      We build strategy, shape platforms, crack big ideas, write campaigns, craft
      treatments, develop films and stay close to production to make sure the
      final thing hits as hard as the first thought.<br /><br />
      When needed, we bring in our own trusted directors, designers, editors and
      specialists and stay on it until it's right.<br /><br />
      We make work that gets stolen. The kind people reference later and pretend
      they thought of first.<br /><br />
      We take on only a few projects at a time. That's how the work lands hard
      and fast.<br /><br />
      We call it Supersonic Creative.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="pillRow">
    <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span> Coming soon</span>
  </div>
</main>

<style>
  .hero {
    --content-w: min(860px, 95vw);
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
    padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 60px);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        900px 600px at 20% 25%,
        rgba(120, 255, 170, 0.08),
        transparent 60%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        900px 600px at 85% 70%,
        rgba(120, 180, 255, 0.06),
        transparent 55%
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: var(--content-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    align-content: center;
    justify-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .logo {
    width: var(--content-w);
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about {
    font-family: "ObviouslyWide", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto,
      Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.2vw, 16px);
    line-height: 1.55;
    width: var(--content-w);
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .pillRow {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #7cffb2;
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(124, 255, 178, 0.55);
  }
</style>
